cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.SY 

This paper discusses the verification of neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, since the paper focuses on the robustness of neural networks, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.CV, which are the sub-categories that deal with machine learning, artificial intelligence, and computer vision, respectively. The sub-categories of cryptography and security (cs.CR) and systems and control (cs.SY) are less likely but still relevant since they deal with security and control of systems, which are important aspects of verifying neural networks.
